    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish with no chips, scratches, or imperfections of any kind. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery still smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear or creasing. Mechanically, it is perfect, with all systems functioning exactly as intended and a complete service history to back it up. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been meticulously preserved and maintained to the highest possible standard.",
