    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for a dedicated mechanic or someone looking for a parts car. The engine currently struggles to start and requires significant diagnostic work, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, there is extensive rust along the rocker panels and wheel wells, and the clear coat is peeling across the hood. The interior shows heavy wear, including several tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It is being sold strictly as-is.",
