      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen in pristine, showroom condition. Every detail reflects uncompromising care, ensuring a driving experience that rivals a new acquisition. This is an investment-grade vehicle for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
